SECTION-BY-SECTION ANALYSIS OF THE LEGISLATION
Section 1. International Boundary and Water Commission Author-
ity
This section authorizes the United States Section of the Inter-
national and Boundary Water Commission to accept funds from a
Federal or non-Federal entity, including through a grant or funding
agreement, to study, design, construct, operate, or maintain waste-
water treatment works, water conservation projects, or flood con-
trol works, and related structures.
